<plot>Shuttling between Sydney and San Francisco this short documentary raises powerful issues regarding HIV/AIDS. The effectiveness of drug cocktails, the benefits of a positive mental attitude and the importance of safe sex are revealed in the true stories of three longtime HIV survivors. One man is on medication, one is recently off medication, and one NEVER took any medication since testing positive twenty-five years ago.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?604337</url></doc>
